### --- Rollback 1: paid-exchange — non-existent exchange (Exchange not found.) ---
# @name rollback1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/paid-exchange
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "exchangeId": 999999,
  "price": 100
}


### --- Rollback 2: match-request — non-existent request (Request not found or not open.) ---
# @name rollback2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/match-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "offerId": 1,
  "requestId": 999999,
  "conversationId": 1,
  "scheduledStart": "2025-03-15 10:00:00",
  "scheduledEnd": "2025-03-15 11:00:00"
}

### --- Rollback 3: "Offer not found." (match-request, valid open requestId 1 but non-existent offerId) ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/match-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "offerId": 999999,
  "requestId": 1,
  "conversationId": 1,
  "scheduledStart": "2025-03-15 10:00:00",
  "scheduledEnd": "2025-03-15 11:00:00"
}

### --- Rollback 4: "Conversation not found." (match-request, valid requestId 1 & offerId 1 but non-existent conversationId) ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/transactions/match-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "offerId": 1,
  "requestId": 1,
  "conversationId": 999999,
  "scheduledStart": "2025-03-15 10:00:00",
  "scheduledEnd": "2025-03-15 11:00:00"
}
